FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://betterreads.me/api/

# Betterreads

Betterreads is an API for scraping book related data

## Book Collection [/books{?limit,offset,filter,sort}]

### List all Books [GET]
+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, Number, `20`) ... max number of records to be returned.
    + offset (optional, Number, `0`) ... the starting point for retrieving data in the list.
    + filter (optional, String, `top`) ... three acceptable values for filter are: 'top', 'series', and 'recent', which respectively result in returning top rated books, books in a series, and most recent books (don't set this parameter for no filtering).
    + sort (optional, String,, `asc`) ... two acceptable values for sort are: 'asc' and 'desc', which result in sorting books by title (don't set this parameter for not sorting).
    
