+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, Number, `20`) ... max number of records to be returned.
    + offset (optional, Number, `0`) ... the starting point for retrieving data in the list.
    + filter (optional, String, `top`) ... the only acceptable value for filter is: 'top', which results in returning top rated authors (don't set this parameter for no filtering).
